prompts.frontCover:
A dynamic comic book panel in a pop art style. In the center, a slightly stressed but heroic-looking cartoon gerbil wearing a tiny superhero cape and mask is running frantically on a giant, spinning hamster wheel. The wheel is depicted as a massive, colorful birthday cake with lit candles whizzing by. Action lines and "POW!" "ZAP!" sound effects in bold, jagged fonts surround the scene. Above the gerbil, a large, stylized speech bubble contains the text.

In the center, in a beautiful, readable, and slightly dramatic handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Trying to keep up with another birthday like..."
